      <header>
                    <h2 class="node__title node-title"><a href="/our-first-batch-its-time-plan-b-shirts-have-been-shipped">Our first batch of &quot;It&#039;s Time for Plan B&quot; shirts have been shipped!</a></h2>
            
              <p class="submitted">
          <span class="authorPic">
		  	  <span class="user-picture">
    <img src="http://timeforplanb.org/sites/default/files/styles/thumbnail/public/pictures/picture-1-1396462673.png?itok=0ctrLm64" alt="TFPB&#039;s picture" title="TFPB&#039;s picture" />  </span>
          </span>
          Submitted by <span class="username">TFPB</span> on <time pubdate datetime="2014-04-10T13:31:13-07:00">Thu, 04/10/2014 - 13:31</time>        </p>
      
          </header>
  
